<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Musketeer Duel - 2 Player Flintlock FPS</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            background: #000;
            overflow: hidden;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
        #gameCanvas {
            display: block;
            width: 100vw;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        #instructions {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
            color: #d4b896;
            padding: 30px 40px;
            border: 3px solid #8b7355;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            z-index: 100;
        }
        #instructions h1 {
            color: #c9a86c;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px #000;
            font-size: 2em;
        }
        .player-controls {
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: top;
            margin: 0 30px;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 15px;
            background: rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.2);
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .player-controls h3 {
            color: #c9a86c;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .player-controls p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .key {
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: bold;
            background: #5a4a3a;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }
        #startBtn {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            font-size: 18px;
            background: #8b4513;
            color: #fff;
            border: 2px solid #c9a86c;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        #startBtn:hover {
            background: #a0522d;
        }
        #ui {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
            display: none;
        }
        .split-line {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 4px;
            background: #8b7355;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
        }
        .player-label {
            position: absolute;
            color: #c9a86c;
            font-size: 14px;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        }
        #p1-label { top: 10px; left: 10px; }
        #p2-label { bottom: 10px; left: 10px; }
        .health-bar {
            position: absolute;
            width: 200px;
            height: 20px;
            background: #333;
            border: 2px solid #8b7355;
        }
        #p1-health { top: 10px; right: 10px; }
        #p2-health { bottom: 10px; right: 10px; }
        .health-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #8b0000, #cd5c5c);
            transition: width 0.3s;
        }
        .reload-status {
            position: absolute;
            right: 10px;
            color: #d4b896;
            font-size: 14px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            padding: 5px 10px;
        }
        #p1-reload { top: 35px; }
        #p2-reload { bottom: 35px; }
        #gameOver {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
            color: #d4b896;
            padding: 40px;
            border: 3px solid #8b7355;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            display: none;
            z-index: 200;
        }
        #winner-text {
            font-size: 2em;
            color: #c9a86c;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        #restartBtn {
            padding: 10px 25px;
            font-size: 16px;
            background: #8b4513;
            color: #fff;
            border: 2px solid #c9a86c;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <canvas id="gameCanvas"></canvas>
    
    <div id="instructions">
        <h1>⚔️ MUSKETEER DUEL ⚔️</h1>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; font-style: italic;">A flintlock duel to the death. No crosshairs - aim with iron sights only.</p>
        
        <div class="player-controls">
            <h3>PLAYER 1 (Top Screen)</h3>
            <p><span class="key">W</span><span class="key">A</span><span class="key">S</span><span class="key">D</span> - Move</p>
            <p><span class="key">T</span><span class="key">F</span><span class="key">G</span><span class="key">H</span> - Look Around</p>
            <p><span class="key">Q</span> - Fire Musket</p>
            <p><span class="key">E</span> - Advance Reload Step</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="player-controls">
            <h3>PLAYER 2 (Bottom Screen)</h3>
            <p><span class="key">↑</span><span class="key">←</span><span class="key">↓</span><span class="key">→</span> - Move</p>
            <p><span class="key">I</span><span class="key">J</span><span class="key">K</span><span class="key">L</span> - Look Around</p>
            <p><span class="key">O</span> - Fire Musket</p>
            <p><span class="key">P</span> - Advance Reload Step</p>
        </div>
        
        <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px; color: #8b7355;">
            Flintlock Reload Sequence: Pour Powder → Place Patch/Ball → Ram Home → Prime Pan → Half-Cock → Full-Cock → FIRE
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #8b7355;">
            Cannot fire while reloading. Iron sights only - align rear notch with front post!
        </p>
        
        <button id="startBtn">ENTER THE FIELD OF HONOR</button>
    </div>
    
    <div id="ui">
        <div class="split-line"></div>
        <div class="player-label" id="p1-label">PLAYER 1</div>
        <div class="player-label" id="p2-label">PLAYER 2</div>
        <div class="health-bar" id="p1-health"><div class="health-fill" id="p1-health-fill" style="width: 100%"></div></div>
        <div class="health-bar" id="p2-health"><div class="health-fill" id="p2-health-fill" style="width: 100%"></div></div>
        <div class="reload-status" id="p1-reload">READY</div>
        <div class="reload-status" id="p2-reload">READY</div>
    </div>
    
    <div id="gameOver">
        <div id="winner-text"></div>
        <button id="restartBtn">Duel Again</button>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/three.js/r128/three.min.js"></script>
    <script src="input.js"></script>
    <script src="ballistics.js"></script>
    <script src="musket.js"></script>
    <script src="player.js"></script>
    <script src="game.js"></script>
</body>
</html>